 and load utility data from the utility clients   integrate utility data with additional data from various 3rd party sources to generate a holistic customer profile   configure and customize opower&rsquo;s energy efficiency software to meet the specific needs of each client   maintain and provide escalated support for the utility energy efficiency programs after launch for the duration of the utility contract   expand the energy efficiency programs from pilot phase to large scale rollout   mentor and train associate professional services engineers     about you      you have a computer-related technical degree and four to seven years of recent, relevant, and deep hands-on technical experience   you live to write programs or scripts to automate tasks and increase efficiency   you are a perfectionist with a knack for sniffing out issues and solving them   you are a sql guru and have extensive experience with large, relational databases, mysql preferred   you have significant and recent linux experience and prefer the command line   you have some high-level programming experience (most of our code is in java, but ruby, perl, python, even vba have their places too)   you are an experienced, high bandwidth engineer, looking for an exciting, high-paced company to further hone your skills and showcase your expertise.     about the company   founded in june 2007, opower creates innovative software products that promote energy efficiency by empowering residential consumers to make better decisions on their energy usage. through a platform which delivers home energy reports, robust online  tools, insights based on data analytics, and customer service tools, opower is reshaping the outlook on home energy demand and achieving unprecedented energy savings across hundreds of thousands of households.  the company is well funded and making big headlines as they stay on track to reach two million households by the end of 2010 and save enough energy to power a city of 150,000 residents!    we do sponsor visas/transfers when applicable.   no phone calls, please. the fastest way to get a response is by sending your resume to the link below.  (if you call then we are just going to ask you to email your resume).   no external recruiters.   "}	{"key":"odAkVfwM"}
